com.alexgilleran.icesoap.xml

Interface XMLParentNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    XMLElement, XMLNode
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    SOAPEnvelope
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseSOAP11Envelope, BaseSOAP12Envelope, BaseSOAPEnvelope, PasswordSOAP11Envelope, XMLParentNodeImpl

    public interface XMLParentNode
extends XMLNode
    Represents an XMLNode - an XML element with zero or more other elements beneath it in the XML hierarchy. Note that this does not represent nodes with text under them, that's the preserve of XMLTextNode.
    Author:
    Alex Gilleran
